# Magnix Cognitive Functions (MCF)

Chi tiết: `.cursor/AGENT_COGNITION.md` · Slash: `.cursor/SLASH_COMMANDS.md` · Parse: `.cursor/JSON_PARSE_LAYER.md` · QA: `.cursor/QA_TIERS.md`.

## Core loop (bắt buộc)

Mọi task không trivial: `INTAKE → ORIENT → ROUTE → PLAN → EXECUTE → SCORE(≥75) → VERIFY → PACKAGE`.

## ROUTE nhanh

- n8n / Google Sheet / Drive / webhook / UID / JSON → **magnix-growth-architect**
- copy / lead magnet / outreach / Q&A / TikTok → **magnix-inbound-copywriter**
- Cả hai → architect (contract) rồi copywriter (prompt)

## VERIFY cứng

- Không secret/PII inline
- Growth: full schema §3.1, parse layer pass
- Copy: QA L0–L3 — `/devil` L2 only; L3 trước publish

## Output

Deliverable theo template trong subagent — không wall of text. Suy luận dài giữ nội bộ; `REFINE` tối đa 1 lần.
